#Brief description of the directory

    app : contain the main app that organize all the mini app (C++)
    hello: contain a basic example of hello world miniapp (C++)
    spike: contain the spike exchange miniapp (C++)
    coreneuron_1.0 : contain 3 mini-app that extract the functionality of CoreNeuron
			- kernel, the main computation of core neuron (C/OMP)
                        - solver, the famous Hines solver for sparse matrix (C)
			- spike, spike exchange (C/MPI)
    utils: a collection of libraries that define common utilities shared by the
           miniapps
                        - storage, a library to handle data loading and sharing
                                   between miniapps

